Pidgin Protocol Status Icons
============================

To install the plugin, simply extract the contents of the folder "pidgin" in this zip file to your pidgin install directory, which is "C:\Program Files\Pidgin" by default, or to your .purple user directory (probably "%APPDATA%\.purple").

Please note that you have copy the themes directory to the .purple user directory of each user if you do a system wide installation into the pidgin install directory.

After activating the plugin you have to choose the plugins default status icon theme (or any other status icon theme that supports this plugin) in "Tools -> Preferences".

Have fun. :o)

